OL,3,CMemorial service held for 450 babies
OL,4,Cfound in unmarked grave
OL,6,FA memorial service has taken place to
OL,7,Fremember almost 500 babies and adults
OL,8,Ffound buried in two unmarked graves.
OL,10,FThe "horrendous" burial site, in
OL,11,FRoyton Cemetery, Oldham, contained the
OL,12,Fbodies of 303 babies - many who had
OL,13,Fbeen stillborn - alongside 27 adults.
OL,15,FAnother, with 159 babies was found
OL,16,Fnext to it.
OL,18,FIt was discovered in the summer by a
OL,19,Fwoman looking for the final resting
OL,20,Fplace of her twin brothers who died 62
OL,21,Fyears ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
