OL,6,FThe "heartfelt" celebration took place
OL,7,Fat the town's St Paul's Church and was
OL,8,Forganised by independent councillor
OL,9,FMaggie Hurley.
OL,11,F"The fact that these babies were taken
OL,12,Ffrom these mothers - many of them
OL,13,Fnever ever held them - they were
OL,14,Ftaken, they were told to get on with
OL,15,Ftheir lives, just forget about it and
OL,16,Fthen put into mass graves like this is
OL,17,Fa social injustice on a level I can
OL,18,Fnever imagine," she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
