OL,3,CMemorial service held for 450 babies
OL,4,Cfound in unmarked grave
OL,6,F"We hope this service leads the way,
OL,7,Fthat other local authorities will do
OL,8,Fthe same, and highlight this more with
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,F"The question has been asked in
OL,12,FWestminster and it will be asked again.
OL,14,F"This is about this government, as
OL,15,Fprevious governments to recognise and
OL,16,Faccept this horrible social injustice,
OL,17,Fto have a national memorial, but
OL,18,Ffirstly to apologise for this.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
