OL,3,CMemorial service held for 450 babies
OL,4,Cfound in unmarked grave
OL,6,F"No one is pointing the finger at
OL,7,Fanybody, this has gone on for 50
OL,8,Fyears, no one is pointing a finger,
OL,9,Fbut what these relatives and mothers
OL,10,Fneed is acceptance, they need to know
OL,11,Fwhere their babies are."
OL,13,FThe babies buried in the graves had
OL,14,Fnot been registered by authorities,
OL,15,Fand it was only when a ledger was
OL,16,Funcovered by Oldham Council, following
OL,17,Fwork by Ms Hurley and her fellow
OL,18,Fcouncillor Jade Hughes, they were able
OL,19,Fto publish the records and inform
OL,20,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
