OL,3,CMemorial service held for 450 babies
OL,4,Cfound in unmarked grave
OL,6,F"I have two brothers in there, they
OL,7,Fwere born and died in 1962, and it's
OL,8,Ftaken until this last couple of months
OL,9,Fto actually find them and I think this
OL,10,Fis a great opportunity to take some
OL,11,Ftime, think about these babies and
OL,12,Fthose that lie with them and to hold
OL,13,Fclose our families."
OL,15,F"I just think we need some honesty,
OL,16,Fsome transparency and some compassion
OL,17,Fand sensitivity about how we share the
OL,18,Fprocess of what took place and how we
OL,19,Freassure people they're there and
OL,20,Fthey're listening and how we find
OL,21,Fthose babies."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
