OL,4,Cfound in unmarked grave
OL,6,FShe echoed calls for the government to
OL,7,Fformally recognise "this practice took
OL,8,Fplace" and urged them to consider a
OL,9,Fnational memorial.
OL,11,F"I'd like an apology for those
OL,12,Fparents, those babies, for all the
OL,13,Fsiblings of those babies, and then I'd
OL,14,Flike some transparency for what took
OL,15,Fplace, why did my mother and all those
OL,16,Fparents have babies taken away from
OL,17,Fthem," she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
