OL,3,CMemorial service held for 450 babies
OL,4,Cfound in unmarked grave
OL,6,F"But I think you have to turn that
OL,7,Finto something positive and look at
OL,8,Fhow we can improve the process for
OL,9,Fpeople to find their babies and make
OL,10,Fsure we have got people there that can
OL,11,Fadvise and help and show people how to
OL,12,Ffind them."
OL,14,FMemorial benches and plinths are being
OL,15,Fplaced in Oldham cemeteries to
OL,16,Fremember babies, children and adults
OL,17,Fwho were buried in unmarked graves.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
