OL,6,FPlinths ` each inscribed with a
OL,7,Fpoignant verse ` and benches where
OL,8,Frelatives and friends can sit
OL,9,Fpeacefully with their thoughts, will
OL,10,Fbe installed at seven council burial
OL,11,Fsites.
OL,13,FBefore the 1980s, stillborns were
OL,14,Ftaken away from families and not given
OL,15,Fany details of where they were buried.
OL,17,FMedical staff would tell bereaved
OL,18,Fparents their children would be buried
OL,19,Falongside "a nice person", but instead
OL,20,Fthe babies were laid to rest in mass
OL,21,Fgraves.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
