OL,6,FOldham Council is also offering
OL,7,Femotional support to relatives who
OL,8,Fhave recently found out loved ones
OL,9,Fwere buried without tributes.
OL,11,FDetails of the burial site in Royton,
OL,12,Fwhich brought this issue to public
OL,13,Fattention, have been available to
OL,14,Fresearch for some time and Council
OL,15,Fstaff have supported many families to
OL,16,Flocate their loved ones over the years.
OL,18,FAnyone can search for their deceased
OL,19,Frelative by using the link on the
OL,20,Fcouncil website.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
