OL,6,FThe grave, numbered 1A-360 in Royton,
OL,7,Fwas first opened in 1924 and the last
OL,8,Fburial took place in 1972, the records
OL,9,Ffor the Royton public graves have now
OL,10,Fall been digitalised, and work is
OL,11,Fongoing for the other records to also
OL,12,Fbe put on line.
OL,14,FFamilies searching for their relatives
OL,15,Fwill need to know the surname and
OL,16,Fapproximate date of death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
